stories: In this paper, we introduce a new transformer network for estimating critical gait parameters from RGB videos captured by a single-view camera. The proposed framework surpasses current state-of-the-art approaches and shows significant improvements in predicting general gait parameters, including walking speed, gait deviation index (GDI), and knee flexion angle at maximum extension. Our approach utilizes fewer parameters and alleviates the need for manual feature extraction.

Our method requires fewer parameters and eliminates the need for manual feature extraction.
